&gt;&gt;

@Dillie17 &lt;&lt; 

- No change in origin and destination or cabin is permitted.
- Rebooking must be done on or before the 31st of December 2022
- New/deferred travel must be on or before the 15th of January 2023

&gt;&gt;

@Dillie17 &lt;&lt; Hence, you will be allowed one free change - no fare difference or change/service fees to be collected subject to the below criteria:

